4
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:16,129
This project will be the e-commerce web application.

5
00:00:16,129 --> 00:00:19,940
So we should define our basic use case analysis.

6
00:00:19,940 --> 00:00:25,400
It is really important to understand what you will develop, and it is crucial that defining your use

7
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:26,150
cases.

8
