14
00:00:58,750 --> 00:01:02,020
Check out the shopping cart and create an order list.

15
00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:05,050
Old orders and order item history.

16
00:01:05,990 --> 00:01:09,800
Now let's identify use cases of our e-commerce application.

